# Project Structure and Conventions

- 루트 패키지: [chainsaws/](mdc:chainsaws/)
- 공통 세션/설정: [chainsaws/aws/shared/](mdc:chainsaws/aws/shared/)
- DynamoDB: [chainsaws/aws/dynamodb/dynamodb.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/dynamodb/dynamodb.py), 내부: [chainsaws/aws/dynamodb/\_dynamodb_internal.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/dynamodb/_dynamodb_internal.py)
- S3: [chainsaws/aws/s3/s3.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/s3/s3.py), 내부: [chainsaws/aws/s3/\_s3_internal.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/s3/_s3_internal.py)
- Lambda: [chainsaws/aws/lambda_client/lambda_client.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/lambda_client/lambda_client.py)
- SQS: [chainsaws/aws/sqs/sqs.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/sqs/sqs.py)
- Scheduler: [chainsaws/aws/scheduler/scheduler.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/scheduler/scheduler.py), 유틸: [chainsaws/aws/scheduler/scheduler_utils.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/scheduler/scheduler_utils.py)
- Secrets Manager: [chainsaws/aws/secrets_manager/secrets_manager.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/secrets_manager/secrets_manager.py)
- SSM: [chainsaws/aws/ssm/ssm.py](mdc:chainsaws/aws/ssm/ssm.py)

패턴:

- High-level 모듈은 반환 형태를 TypedDict/데이터클래스로 정규화.
- Low-level `_*_internal.py`는 boto3 thin wrapper (가능한 원형 유지).
- README 예제와 실제 시그니처 항상 동기화.
